01:01:10.980 --> 01:01:13.950 align:middle line:90%


01:01:13.950 --> 01:01:17.415 align:middle line:90%
Well--

01:01:17.415 --> 01:01:19.910 align:middle line:90%


01:01:19.910 --> 01:01:22.690 align:middle line:90%
Let's talk about it.

01:01:22.690 --> 01:01:24.158 align:middle line:90%
LUKE: No, I just need some time.

01:01:24.158 --> 01:01:36.742 align:middle line:90%


01:01:36.742 --> 01:01:39.454 align:middle line:84%
Do you want me to
scramble you some eggs?

01:01:39.454 --> 01:01:41.402 align:middle line:90%
LUKE: That would be nice.

01:01:41.402 --> 01:01:42.376 align:middle line:90%
How many?

01:01:42.376 --> 01:01:45.310 align:middle line:90%


01:01:45.310 --> 01:01:46.055 align:middle line:90%
300.

01:01:46.055 --> 01:01:47.915 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHTER]

01:01:47.915 --> 01:01:48.800 align:middle line:90%
I love you.

01:01:48.800 --> 01:02:10.890 align:middle line:90%


01:02:10.890 --> 01:02:11.630 align:middle line:90%
Are you scared?

01:02:11.630 --> 01:02:17.390 align:middle line:90%


01:02:17.390 --> 01:02:18.350 align:middle line:90%
I am.

01:02:18.350 --> 01:02:21.710 align:middle line:90%


01:02:21.710 --> 01:02:25.840 align:middle line:90%
Not a lot, but a little.

01:02:25.840 --> 01:02:47.640 align:middle line:90%


01:02:47.640 --> 01:02:49.030 align:middle line:90%
Please let me in.

01:02:49.030 --> 01:03:00.162 align:middle line:90%


01:03:00.162 --> 01:03:01.410 align:middle line:84%
LUKE: Yeah, you're
probably right.

01:03:01.410 --> 01:03:03.241 align:middle line:84%
I just need some time
off, get away someplace.

01:03:03.241 --> 01:03:04.440 align:middle line:84%
Well, it's probably
not a bad idea.

01:03:04.440 --> 01:03:05.600 align:middle line:90%
Hm.

01:03:05.600 --> 01:03:07.080 align:middle line:84%
I mean, Tony can
do extra hours now.

01:03:07.080 --> 01:03:09.080 align:middle line:84%
And anyway, I think we
should be looking at--

01:03:09.080 --> 01:03:11.380 align:middle line:84%
You know, she even
made me scrambled eggs.

01:03:11.380 --> 01:03:13.130 align:middle line:90%
I'm sorry I got so drunk.

01:03:13.130 --> 01:03:14.580 align:middle line:90%
You should be, you bastard.

01:03:14.580 --> 01:03:15.455 align:middle line:90%
Yeah.

01:03:15.455 --> 01:03:16.200 align:middle line:90%
Everything's fine.

01:03:16.200 --> 01:03:17.400 align:middle line:90%
I'm just under a lot of stress.

01:03:17.400 --> 01:03:19.030 align:middle line:90%
I've stopped hyp-- just stand.

01:03:19.030 --> 01:03:19.976 align:middle line:90%
What are you doing?

01:03:19.976 --> 01:03:21.395 align:middle line:84%
Don't-- don't talk.
Don't talk.

01:03:21.395 --> 01:03:24.233 align:middle line:90%
Hey, Luke.

01:03:24.233 --> 01:03:26.620 align:middle line:84%
Oh, this is my
partner, business

01:03:26.620 --> 01:03:27.920 align:middle line:90%
partner at the clinic, Hugh.

01:03:27.920 --> 01:03:30.555 align:middle line:84%
Yeah, um, actually,
a good friend of mine

01:03:30.555 --> 01:03:31.900 align:middle line:90%
comes and sees you.

01:03:31.900 --> 01:03:33.060 align:middle line:90%
She recommended.

01:03:33.060 --> 01:03:34.155 align:middle line:90%
Who's your friend?

01:03:34.155 --> 01:03:35.890 align:middle line:90%
Um, Lisa Wells.

01:03:35.890 --> 01:03:37.363 align:middle line:84%
-And you are?
