01:03:37.363 --> 01:03:41.429 align:middle line:84%
Nice to meet you.
-Nice to meet you.

01:03:41.429 --> 01:03:43.120 align:middle line:84%
Uh, do you work
around here, Amelia?

01:03:43.120 --> 01:03:45.440 align:middle line:90%
Uh, yeah, just up there.

01:03:45.440 --> 01:03:48.290 align:middle line:90%


01:03:48.290 --> 01:03:50.190 align:middle line:90%
Well, I-- I'd better go.

01:03:50.190 --> 01:03:51.615 align:middle line:90%
Lovely to meet you.

01:03:51.615 --> 01:03:52.565 align:middle line:90%
Yeah, you, too.

01:03:52.565 --> 01:03:56.340 align:middle line:84%
Hey, um, wink
three times if it's

01:03:56.340 --> 01:03:59.220 align:middle line:90%
bad news, two if it's good?

01:03:59.220 --> 01:04:02.145 align:middle line:84%
Um-- look, I'm-- I
can't wink anyways.

01:04:02.145 --> 01:04:04.510 align:middle line:84%
It's-- it's like
a genetic thing.

01:04:04.510 --> 01:04:09.890 align:middle line:84%
I just-- roll my tongue and that
one, but I can't blink at all.

01:04:09.890 --> 01:04:12.830 align:middle line:84%
Well, I can blink,
but I can't wink.

01:04:12.830 --> 01:04:13.620 align:middle line:90%
That one.

01:04:13.620 --> 01:04:14.480 align:middle line:90%
There.

01:04:14.480 --> 01:04:17.480 align:middle line:84%
-Can you do this, Hugh?
-No.

01:04:17.480 --> 01:04:21.610 align:middle line:84%
No, no, I have my
dignity to think of.

01:04:21.610 --> 01:04:23.388 align:middle line:84%
Well, if you're not going
to wink, I'll-- I'll go.

01:04:23.388 --> 01:04:26.382 align:middle line:84%
So it was lovely to meet you.
-Likewise.

01:04:26.382 --> 01:05:19.860 align:middle line:90%


01:05:19.860 --> 01:05:21.060 align:middle line:90%
Can I see you for a moment?

01:05:21.060 --> 01:05:22.090 align:middle line:90%
Yeah, sure.

01:05:22.090 --> 01:05:23.980 align:middle line:84%
-What's this?
-What's it look like?

01:05:23.980 --> 01:05:25.231 align:middle line:90%
You're disgusting.

01:05:25.231 --> 01:05:26.800 align:middle line:90%
It's not mine.

01:05:26.800 --> 01:05:28.000 align:middle line:90%
I'm your employer.

01:05:28.000 --> 01:05:29.850 align:middle line:84%
You can't-- can you
talk to me about this?

01:05:29.850 --> 01:05:31.060 align:middle line:90%
Whoa, you're brave.

01:05:31.060 --> 01:05:32.910 align:middle line:84%
It's not mine-- why
don't you blame him?

01:05:32.910 --> 01:05:33.655 align:middle line:90%
Why do you blame me?

01:05:33.655 --> 01:05:35.895 align:middle line:84%
It's called process
of elimination, Luke.

01:05:35.895 --> 01:05:37.780 align:middle line:84%
Had to have one of you and
you're acting really weird.

01:05:37.780 --> 01:05:39.764 align:middle line:90%
Maybe it's Tony's.

01:05:39.764 --> 01:05:41.240 align:middle line:90%
SANDY: Ugh.

01:05:41.240 --> 01:05:42.560 align:middle line:90%
You are in trouble.

01:05:42.560 --> 01:05:44.070 align:middle line:90%
Can I have a look at that?

01:05:44.070 --> 01:05:45.502 align:middle line:90%
You're disgusting.

01:05:45.502 --> 01:05:48.450 align:middle line:84%
SANDY: And by the way, Ms.
Browne's results came in.

01:05:48.450 --> 01:06:45.222 align:middle line:90%


01:06:45.222 --> 01:06:48.026 align:middle line:84%
-Good morning.
-Jesus.

01:06:48.026 --> 01:06:52.510 align:middle line:90%


01:06:52.510 --> 01:06:53.400 align:middle line:90%
What are you doing here?

01:06:53.400 --> 01:06:56.060 align:middle line:90%


01:06:56.060 --> 01:06:57.120 align:middle line:90%
Catching up on some work.

01:06:57.120 --> 01:06:59.820 align:middle line:90%


01:06:59.820 --> 01:07:01.200 align:middle line:90%
I mean in my seat.

01:07:01.200 --> 01:07:04.630 align:middle line:90%


01:07:04.630 --> 01:07:07.570 align:middle line:84%
-Oh.
-Get out.

01:07:07.570 --> 01:07:13.940 align:middle line:90%


01:07:13.940 --> 01:07:15.920 align:middle line:90%
Are you always this scary?

01:07:15.920 --> 01:07:18.860 align:middle line:90%
Pretty much.

01:07:18.860 --> 01:07:20.330 align:middle line:90%
I'll get you a coffee.

01:07:20.330 --> 01:07:21.310 align:middle line:90%
You look like crap.

01:07:21.310 --> 01:07:26.700 align:middle line:90%


01:07:26.700 --> 01:07:29.323 align:middle line:90%
[PHONE RINGING]

01:07:29.323 --> 01:07:39.174 align:middle line:90%


01:07:39.174 --> 01:07:40.605 align:middle line:90%
AMELIA: Sorry, I'm early.

01:07:40.605 --> 01:07:41.559 align:middle line:90%
LUKE: No, it's fine.

01:07:41.559 --> 01:07:42.900 align:middle line:90%
Please come in, sit down.

01:07:42.900 --> 01:07:47.880 align:middle line:90%


01:07:47.880 --> 01:07:50.868 align:middle line:84%
How do you feel?
-Nervous.

01:07:50.868 --> 01:07:54.354 align:middle line:90%


01:07:54.354 --> 01:07:56.150 align:middle line:84%
Yeah, the-- well, the
results have come in

01:07:56.150 --> 01:08:00.500 align:middle line:90%
and, uh, they could be better.

01:08:00.500 --> 01:08:01.280 align:middle line:90%
How much better?

01:08:01.280 --> 01:08:04.542 align:middle line:90%


01:08:04.542 --> 01:08:07.370 align:middle line:84%
The lump will
need to be removed.

01:08:07.370 --> 01:08:10.493 align:middle line:84%
Uh, the cells were
found to be malignant.

01:08:10.493 --> 01:08:13.874 align:middle line:90%


01:08:13.874 --> 01:08:16.772 align:middle line:90%
AMELIA: OK.

01:08:16.772 --> 01:08:19.187 align:middle line:90%
Then what?

01:08:19.187 --> 01:08:23.540 align:middle line:84%
Uh, then, well, yeah, if
you mean after the operation,

01:08:23.540 --> 01:08:26.520 align:middle line:84%
then-- then there's many
paths that you can go down,

01:08:26.520 --> 01:08:30.609 align:middle line:84%
and chemotherapy is
only one of those paths.

01:08:30.609 --> 01:08:32.899 align:middle line:84%
And here at the clinic,
we-- we do all sorts

01:08:32.899 --> 01:08:34.419 align:middle line:84%
of treatments for all
sorts of conditions

01:08:34.419 --> 01:08:37.800 align:middle line:90%
that are a lot less intrusive.

01:08:37.800 --> 01:08:41.469 align:middle line:84%
I know it's not the only way,
but it is-- it's a good option

01:08:41.469 --> 01:08:42.753 align:middle line:90%
and I know that it works.

01:08:42.753 --> 01:08:48.110 align:middle line:90%


01:08:48.110 --> 01:08:50.058 align:middle line:90%
I'm sorry.

01:08:50.058 --> 01:08:52.006 align:middle line:90%
Um.

01:08:52.006 --> 01:08:53.742 align:middle line:84%
I should go.
-Please.

01:08:53.742 --> 01:08:55.415 align:middle line:84%
Um--
-No.

01:08:55.415 --> 01:08:56.399 align:middle line:90%
Please don't.

01:08:56.399 --> 01:09:00.010 align:middle line:90%
Please-- please stay.

01:09:00.010 --> 01:09:07.252 align:middle line:84%
Amelia, um, I need to explain
to you what happens next--

01:09:07.252 --> 01:09:08.140 align:middle line:90%


01:09:08.140 --> 01:09:10.072 align:middle line:84%
What we need to look
at, what you need to do.

01:09:10.072 --> 01:09:14.732 align:middle line:90%


01:09:14.732 --> 01:09:19.390 align:middle line:90%
AMELIA: The strange thing is--

01:09:19.390 --> 01:09:20.370 align:middle line:90%


01:09:20.370 --> 01:09:22.946 align:middle line:84%
If it was just cancer--
and that's what I think

01:09:22.946 --> 01:09:25.875 align:middle line:90%
you're telling me here, right?

01:09:25.875 --> 01:09:28.677 align:middle line:90%
I don't know.

01:09:28.677 --> 01:09:31.219 align:middle line:90%
It's sort of be OK.

01:09:31.219 --> 01:09:34.924 align:middle line:90%
Not OK, but at least private.

01:09:34.924 --> 01:09:42.090 align:middle line:90%


01:09:42.090 --> 01:09:48.892 align:middle line:84%
Hey, um, I don't have any
more appointments on, if you

01:09:48.892 --> 01:09:54.205 align:middle line:90%
want to-- I don't know--

01:09:54.205 --> 01:09:57.103 align:middle line:90%


01:09:57.103 --> 01:09:58.610 align:middle line:84%
What if I don't
go through with it?

01:09:58.610 --> 01:10:01.430 align:middle line:90%


01:10:01.430 --> 01:10:02.880 align:middle line:90%
Why would you do that?

01:10:02.880 --> 01:10:06.170 align:middle line:90%
Well, how long do I have?

01:10:06.170 --> 01:10:09.480 align:middle line:84%
Uh, I'm-- I'm always wary
of giving time predictions,

01:10:09.480 --> 01:10:10.577 align:middle line:90%
especially in your case.

01:10:10.577 --> 01:10:12.110 align:middle line:84%
There's lots of other
tests that needs to be--

01:10:12.110 --> 01:10:14.790 align:middle line:84%
No, two, three,
four weeks, months?

01:10:14.790 --> 01:10:17.860 align:middle line:84%
Amelia, no, as your
doctor, I strongly

01:10:17.860 --> 01:10:20.645 align:middle line:84%
recommend that you don't
consider that as an option.

01:10:20.645 --> 01:10:23.884 align:middle line:90%
What about as men?

01:10:23.884 --> 01:10:25.750 align:middle line:90%
What?

01:10:25.750 --> 01:10:26.860 align:middle line:90%
Tell me.

01:10:26.860 --> 01:10:28.810 align:middle line:90%
Tell me you'd fine your wife--

01:10:28.810 --> 01:10:31.280 align:middle line:90%
Wife to be.

01:10:31.280 --> 01:10:35.180 align:middle line:84%
Tell me you'd find your
wife to be as attractive

01:10:35.180 --> 01:10:37.580 align:middle line:90%
or as desirable if she was--

01:10:37.580 --> 01:10:38.526 align:middle line:90%
Of course I would.

01:10:38.526 --> 01:10:44.202 align:middle line:90%


01:10:44.202 --> 01:10:45.830 align:middle line:90%
Did you buy that dress?

01:10:45.830 --> 01:10:54.416 align:middle line:90%


01:10:54.416 --> 01:10:57.754 align:middle line:84%
AMELIA (VOICEOVER): So are
excited about the wedding?

01:10:57.754 --> 01:10:58.520 align:middle line:90%
LUKE (VOICEOVER): Yeah.

01:10:58.520 --> 01:11:02.360 align:middle line:90%


01:11:02.360 --> 01:11:04.690 align:middle line:90%
Nervous.

01:11:04.690 --> 01:11:08.161 align:middle line:84%
In a couple weeks,
you'll be relieved.

01:11:08.161 --> 01:11:08.860 align:middle line:90%
You'll see.

01:11:08.860 --> 01:11:11.430 align:middle line:90%


01:11:11.430 --> 01:11:14.142 align:middle line:90%
So is it a big wedding?

01:11:14.142 --> 01:11:16.114 align:middle line:90%
No.

01:11:16.114 --> 01:11:17.593 align:middle line:90%
50 people or so.

01:11:17.593 --> 01:11:25.974 align:middle line:90%


01:11:25.974 --> 01:11:29.219 align:middle line:84%
Do you have family
here that can--

01:11:29.219 --> 01:11:29.918 align:middle line:90%
No.

01:11:29.918 --> 01:11:33.369 align:middle line:90%


01:11:33.369 --> 01:11:34.848 align:middle line:84%
You promise not
to talk about it.

01:11:34.848 --> 01:11:38.586 align:middle line:90%


01:11:38.586 --> 01:11:39.285 align:middle line:90%
Not now.

01:11:39.285 --> 01:11:45.201 align:middle line:90%


01:11:45.201 --> 01:11:48.090 align:middle line:90%
Do you know what's weird?

01:11:48.090 --> 01:11:49.937 align:middle line:84%
You know how people
say they can't

01:11:49.937 --> 01:11:53.913 align:middle line:90%
believe it's happening to them?

01:11:53.913 --> 01:12:00.235 align:middle line:84%
Well, I really can't believe
this is happening to me.

01:12:00.235 --> 01:12:04.060 align:middle line:90%
I'm only 30.

01:12:04.060 --> 01:12:07.080 align:middle line:90%
30 what?

01:12:07.080 --> 01:12:08.980 align:middle line:90%
Something.

01:12:08.980 --> 01:12:11.360 align:middle line:90%
I'm in the gap.

01:12:11.360 --> 01:12:13.285 align:middle line:90%
The gap?

01:12:13.285 --> 01:12:16.750 align:middle line:90%
Reinvention gap.

01:12:16.750 --> 01:12:21.315 align:middle line:84%
Um, it's sort of, well, it's
still there, but in a way

01:12:21.315 --> 01:12:28.100 align:middle line:84%
it's a time where you
can change, make choices

01:12:28.100 --> 01:12:42.032 align:middle line:84%
to-- you can change yourself or,
um, do anything, meet someone.

01:12:42.032 --> 01:12:44.893 align:middle line:84%
Why would you want
to reinvent yourself?

01:12:44.893 --> 01:12:48.362 align:middle line:84%
Uh, because--
because I want to be

01:12:48.362 --> 01:12:50.370 align:middle line:90%
the person I know I am inside.

01:12:50.370 --> 01:12:53.840 align:middle line:90%


01:12:53.840 --> 01:12:56.690 align:middle line:84%
What makes you think
you know what you feel

01:12:56.690 --> 01:12:59.110 align:middle line:90%
inside isn't how you appear?

01:12:59.110 --> 01:13:09.521 align:middle line:84%
Oh, because, uh, sometimes I
don't know what to say in front

01:13:09.521 --> 01:13:13.609 align:middle line:84%
of people and the
lines shrivel up

01:13:13.609 --> 01:13:16.580 align:middle line:84%
and it always happens
in the most critical

01:13:16.580 --> 01:13:19.110 align:middle line:90%
situations possible, you know?

01:13:19.110 --> 01:13:22.340 align:middle line:84%
And then I get home and sort
of slap myself for not saying

01:13:22.340 --> 01:13:24.396 align:middle line:84%
anything or sticking
up for myself,

01:13:24.396 --> 01:13:28.830 align:middle line:84%
or-- yeah, well,
it's just pathetic.

01:13:28.830 --> 01:13:32.110 align:middle line:84%
-Oh, I think we all do that one.
-Really?

01:13:32.110 --> 01:13:33.030 align:middle line:90%
Do you?

01:13:33.030 --> 01:13:34.620 align:middle line:90%
Mm.

01:13:34.620 --> 01:13:35.601 align:middle line:90%
Yeah, yeah.

01:13:35.601 --> 01:13:38.898 align:middle line:90%
I don't melt. I, um, I freeze.

01:13:38.898 --> 01:13:42.195 align:middle line:90%
Oh, all right.

01:13:42.195 --> 01:13:45.346 align:middle line:84%
Is that what you were doing
the other day when I met you?

01:13:45.346 --> 01:13:47.816 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHTER]

